1. *Top* je najjači instrument u vojsci. (The cannon is the strongest weapon in the army.)
2. *Topići* se u dubokoj vodi može biti opasno. (Drowning in deep water can be dangerous.)
3. Ovo je *top* destinacija za ljubitelje skijanja. (This is a top destination for skiing enthusiasts.)
4. Moramo *toplo* preporučiti ovaj restoran, hrana je fantastična. (We must warmly recommend this restaurant, the food is fantastic.)
5. *Topli* napitak mi je omiljeni deo zimskih večeri. (A warm beverage is my favorite part of winter evenings.)
6. *Topovski udar* je izazvao veliku štetu na gradskoj infrastrukturi. (The cannon strike caused significant damage to the city infrastructure.)
7. *Toplo* vreme u februaru je iznenadilo sve. (The warm weather in February surprised everyone.)
8. *Toplo* se obucite, napolju je hladno. (Dress warmly, it's cold outside.)
9. *Toplina* sunčevih zraka učinila je dan savršenim za izlet u prirodu. (The warmth of the sun's rays made the day perfect for a nature trip.)
10. *Topovska paljba* je trajala satima. (The cannon fire lasted for hours.)